{"about_the_game":"Multiplayer deathmatch games with drones!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy fast multiplayer action with your drone in Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch competitions in exotic arenas.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArena is a game from the creators of Drone Fighters. Although it\u2019s a very different kind of game, your avatars and drones will be synced across both games if you play them. Just like Drone Fighters, Arena is also supporting cross platform play between non-VR PC, Vive and Oculus players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere are 2 types of competitions in this Early Access version, Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch. We will be adding new modes with upcoming patches. Game controls are tuned to the platform, and we\u2019ve tried to make it fun whatever your device of choice to play Arena.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs in all Surreal powered games, you can customize your drone and avatar in great detail, and use the same configuration for all our other games. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nJoin the community and share your thoughts and feedback. We want you to be part of the development process.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Ten Games Played","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/655200/c999681b64572829bcaabbcfa2b45c8a5126e6c8.jpg"},{"name":"Fifty Games Played","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/655200/37cd66103eefe532d86a6c0c646fb803b918ec0a.jpg"},{"name":"One Hundred Games Played","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/655200/ca8a445dc186973488675300a1640b6b17b8f7c5.jpg"},{"name":"Deathmatch Win","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/655200/cf6f20495613801427fe7d70934b5386a6f4ee21.jpg"},{"name":"Five Deathmatch Wins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/655200/9e39281f241ca77fb10564ab6be6f3464dd5fbb5.jpg"},{"name":"Twenty Five Deathmatch Wins","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/